short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extend the capabilities of ApyHub Fusion with this extension

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Power up ApyHub Fusion with this extension.

It allows you to test your applications running remotely or locally by removing the CORS restrictions. 

ApyHub Fusion is an powerful yet simple tool that allows developers to design, mock, test and document your APIs. It also comes integrated with the huge catalog of ApyHub services.
